## Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- Python {{ python_version }}+
- [UV](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) package manager
- [go-task](https://taskfile.dev/) task runner
- [pnpm](https://pnpm.io/) for frontend
- {{ container_runtime }} for containers

### Setup

`ash
# Install dependencies
task backend:dev

# Start development server
uv run uvicorn {{ project_slug }}.main:app --reload

# Or use containers
task docker:up
`

### Development Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| 	ask backend:dev | Install Python dependencies |
| 	ask backend:test | Run test suite via tox |
| 	ask backend:lint | Run linters (Ruff) |
| 	ask backend:format | Auto-format code |
| 	ask backend:typecheck | Run mypy type checker |
| 	ask frontend:dev | Start frontend dev server |
| 	ask frontend:test | Run frontend tests |
| 	ask docker:up | Start all containers |
| 	ask docker:down | Stop all containers |

### API Documentation

- Swagger UI: http://localhost:8000/api/docs
- ReDoc: http://localhost:8000/api/redoc

